data.description: Situated next to North Hills Neighborhood known for the Dogwood Trail, this mid-mod home fits right in with its own Dogwood tree and landscaped yard. The unique architecture could be in a magazine, but don't let the mid-mod vibes fool you. She was remodeled in 2021 and sports a newer roof, windows, bathrooms, and floors throughout. Speaking of the interior, let's head inside, shall we? If you park in the carport, you'll pop right into the kitchen, making both grocery shopping & entertaining a breeze. Past the kitchen, you'll meander straight into the living room and continue to one of TWO patios. (The first one is in the front with built-in flower boxes filled with lavender and the side one is perfect for  grilling on summer nights.) Back inside, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, including a master with two closets and an ensuite bathroom. Speaking of spacious, this beaut also hosts a large basement with gobs of storage and a laundry room (Yes, you heard that right! A laundry ROOM). While the upstairs is perfect for chatting with friends while burgers are on the grill, the basement is perfect for cozy movie nights and blanket forts. And again, all this mid-mod beauty is tucked right next to the enviable North Hills neighborhood, home to the Dogwood Trail and blooms for days. This home is truly dreamy... are you ready for it to be your reality?? **Buyer to verify all information**
